Package sos.mlq.io

Class FileParser

java.lang.Object
sos.mlq.io.FileParser
public class FileParser extends Object
Reads process data from a text file and converts each line into a Process object for the MLQ scheduler. Expected format per line: label; burstTime; arrivalTime; queue Example: A;6;0;1 B;9;0;1 C;10;0;2 D;15;0;2 E;8;0;3 Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
